# UI Design System

The interface should feel like a premium SaaS dashboard.

Design inspiration

- Apple
- Notion
- Stripe
- Linear
- Airbnb
- Vercel Dashboard

Style

- Minimal
- Spacious
- Professional
- Luxury
- Modern

Never overcrowd pages.

Every page should have

- Header
- Breadcrumb
- Search
- Filters
- Action Buttons
- Responsive Cards
- Empty State
- Loading Skeleton
- Error State

